                "quality_rating": 5
            },
            {
                "comment": "Was an excellently designed class with just the right amount of theory, thermodynamics and application. His competence showed through; he took any question you could ask and made sure you got it. Homework ensures you understand what's going on but you can breeze through them. Strongly recommend this course to anybody.",
